This extension provides native support for the FIN|Stack Graphics application. It will enable features in the application that are not available within a simple browser context.

FIN|Stack is a next generation Building Automation System software suite, utilizing browser based BAS applications and server technology.  It leverages built-in tagging and data modeling, enabling unprecedented new functionality and automating much of the traditional workflow, thus reducing engineering labor and the complexity of engineering a project.
